esture should be disabled - Close button (if any) should be disabled or hidden - UI should show a clear loading indicator - Drawer closes automatically only after successful submission (or stays open on error) ## Context - File: pages/PublicMenu/base/CartView.jsx - Related state: likely an `isSubmitting` / `isLoading` boolean flag already exists for the submit button - The fix should use this existing flag to gate close gestures - Check if the drawer close handler is passed as a prop (e.g., `onClose`) — it should be wrapped: `if (!isSubmitting) onClose()` - Also check the drag handle / swipe gesture handler for the same guard - Do NOT change the overall drawer architecture — minimal targeted fix only === END ===
